# Local dev: Vite proxies /parties to PartyKit (default port 1999).
# Only set this if PartyKit is on a different port:
# PARTYKIT_DEV_PORT=60142

# Production build: your deployed PartyKit host (no https://).
# Must match `npx partykit deploy --domain ...` (CI uses party.jaronerba.com).
# VITE_PARTYKIT_HOST=party.jaronerba.com

# Optional room password for PartyKit (set on the PartyKit project, not Pages):
#   npx partykit env set ROOM_KEY your-secret-here
# ROOM_KEY is read by partykit/server.ts as env "room-key".
